    "description": "During the stone age things were settled in a more simple and direct manner. Brawl with your friends in the arena or work together to throw your enemies out of the ring. But don’t forget to use the destructible arena as a weapon! It doesn’t matter what type of player you are, tactician or button-smasher, you will have your chance at victory! <br><br>BRAWLING <br>Meet other players in the arena and fight for victory. Knock your enemies off the platform by hitting them with your mighty club, the last caveman standing wins! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/49758c72950e845bea96defc540a322b.poster.avif?t=1717754335\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/49758c72950e845bea96defc540a322b.webm?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/49758c72950e845bea96defc540a322b.mp4?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>DESTRUCTIBLE ARENAS<br>Smash the floor and reshape the battleground. The floor of the arena is destructible, use it to give yourself an advantage! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/bd4abad1fd20b923e72c31699ed3e057.poster.avif?t=1717754335\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/bd4abad1fd20b923e72c31699ed3e057.webm?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/bd4abad1fd20b923e72c31699ed3e057.mp4?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>FUN &amp; CHAOS<br>Many different playstyles and strategies make every match unique. Embrace the chaotic and ever changing club frenzy and experience the fun with your fellow cavemen!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/00f4ab905d0e24179b0cc132a0047110.poster.avif?t=1717754335\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/00f4ab905d0e24179b0cc132a0047110.webm?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/00f4ab905d0e24179b0cc132a0047110.mp4?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>CUSTOMIZE<br>Change how you look by changing outfits, weapons, armor and tattoos. Create your very own caveman!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/2eeb9016608a4ea9f2c8737ec9096b2c.poster.avif?t=1717754335\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/2eeb9016608a4ea9f2c8737ec9096b2c.webm?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/2eeb9016608a4ea9f2c8737ec9096b2c.mp4?t=1717754335\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>STORE<br>Get the weapons, armors and many other things you like from our ingame store. All items are visual only and will not have any influence on your stats or gameplay.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875100/extras/c06a590396bb1a5a9ab0493d2ef6890c.poster.avif?t=1717754335\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.s